		<h2 class="subheading">Selling to Charlie - Selling to CEO's and Top Management</h2>
		<p class="dynamic-p">Selling to CEO's, and other top managers, shortens the sales cycle, extends relationships, and increases sales. That is why salespeople must know how to successfully sell to this critical segment of their customer base. Unfortunately most salespeople don't know how to, or are afraid to, sell to the CEO, CFO, or COO. After participating in Sean's "Selling to Charlie" speech, every attendee will leave with their target, objective, and specific steps on how to succeed.</p>
